    public class JEnumConstant
extends AbstractJExpressionImpl
implements IJDeclaration, IJAnnotatable, IJDocCommentable
    Enum Constant. When used as an IJExpression, this object represents a reference to the enum constant.
    Author:
    Bhakti Mehta (Bhakti.Mehta@sun.com)
